      "span_text": "SLC35F3 expression-The human SLC35F3 full-length cDNA (Unigene Hs. 158748, RefSeq mRNA XM_001132419.1, Image clone 5273868, NCBI accession BC037878.1, IRAK75-e24) was obtained from Geneservice Ltd. <http://www.geneservice.co.uk> in pBluescript-R, and subcloned into the prokaryotic expression plasmid pZE12luc"
